    "body": "#1252 \n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **Refactor**\n  * Backward kernel refactored to process data in block-wise tiles, improving memory locality and compute efficiency for sparse attention backward pass.\n\n* **Tests**\n  * Added a larger-scale test case to validate backward kernel behavior with increased sequence/height sizes.\n\n<sub>✏️ Tip: You can customize this high-level summary in your review settings.</sub>\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
